bios.resume:
Diana Rodriguez is a Full Stack Developer/DevOps & Google Developer Expert. With 18 years' experience and a strong background in back end and infrastructure, Diana likes to bring together the best of both worlds, spreading DevOps culture.

Skills: Java, Python, Node.js, GCP, AWS, Kubernetes, Automation and many more amazing tools.
